    <div class="card border-0 shadow-sm mb-4">
      <div class="card-body">
        <h2 class="h4 mb-3">1. AI-assisted workflow: Antigravity + Codex + Claude Code</h2>
        <p>In this workflow, AI acts as an engineering pair-programmer. The human sets priorities and approves output. AI helps with code edits, refactoring, translation, styling fixes, and implementation speed.</p>
        <p><strong>Antigravity</strong> is used here as an AI-assisted development workflow: define goals, break tasks into clear iterations, and validate each change before publishing.</p>
        <p><strong>Codex</strong> is a coding agent that can edit project files, run commands, and apply targeted patches quickly. It is useful for consistent technical execution in iterative website work.</p>
        <p><strong>Claude Code</strong> can play a similar partner role: drafting alternatives, refining structure and copy, and helping validate implementation approaches from another angle.</p>
        <p class="mb-0">In plain terms: AI does not replace the whole build process by magic. It speeds up implementation cycles while the developer stays in control of decisions and quality.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

